        en: >-
          The Spring Season Card for 2026 is inspired by an illustrative
          flat-lay style. Hand-painted and viewed from a bird’s-eye perspective,
          with a soft, matt texture. It evokes the perfect spring day, when
          you’re having a picnic brunch in the park with friends. Add some fresh
          coffee, and spring can come.
